{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "The pretraining corpus is disjoint from the annotated corpus.",
    "We conducted the following preprocessing steps: each letter was converted into a UTF-8 encoded raw text file using the LibreOffice command line tool soffice (version 6.2.8).",
    "We chose LibreOffice, as it best preserved the structure of newlines and blanklines.",
    "We automatically de-identified all letters using a method based on a deep learning model trained on internal data, see Richter-Pechanski et al. (2019).",
    "We replaced PHI tokens with semantic surrogates, see Lohr et al. (2021)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
